headline.print_headline: US and Britain Reject East-West Divide in Ukraine
headline.main: US and Britain Reject East-West Divide in Ukraine

lead_paragraph: The United States and Britain on Tuesday rejected suggestions that the ouster of Ukraine's pro-Russia president and the politics around it are representative of a Cold War-era East-West divide.
